Text: i love the fact that the same wrong information gets listed on torrents rapidshare files etc. ive downloaded 3 different copies of this and Dennis Miller isnt in any of them. its the girl from prime suspect and a bloke from New Girl (i think). Still craig at his entertaining best
The guy at the end should have won the Golden Mouth Organ based on the crappy playing by Zooey who whined that Craig wasn't going to give it to her.
it's the last show but it's not Dennis Miller, guests are Maria Bello and Jake Johnson.
